---Files---

Makefile             - GNU makefile to build all relevant code
README               - 当前文件
encfuse.h            - 用户态文件系统加密头文件
encfuse.c            - 用户态文件系统加密文件
file-crypt.h         - 国密加密头文件
file-crypt.c         - 国密加密文件
access-control.h     - 访问控制头文件
access-control.c     - 访问控制文件

---Dependencies---

```
yum install attr

yum install -y gcc gcc-c++

yum install make

yum install -y openssl openssl-devel

yum install -y fuse fuse-devel
```

---prepare---

cd encfuse
mkdir .secret && cd .secret
touch user
touch process
cd ..
chmod 700 .secret

打开 /etc/fuse.conf 文件
将user_allow_other选项开启

---Examples---

***Building***

Build All:
  make

Clean:
  make clean

***FUSE Examples***

挂载参数：
  ./encfuse <flags> ... <mount directory> <mirror directory> <keyphrase>
示例挂载:
  ./encfuse ./mnt ./test 12345
挂载并允许其他用户访问:
  ./encfuse -o allow_other ./mnt ./test 12345
绑定stdout和stderr流:
  ./encfuse -f ./mnt ./test 12345
取消挂载:
  fusermount -u <Mount Point>
  umount <Mount Point>
强制取消挂载
  ps aux | grep "mnt"
  kill -9 pid
  umount -l <Mount Point>
  

***查看挂载信息***

mount

cat /proc/mounts | grep "mnt"

---warning---

若挂载目录不为空，会报错：

fuse: mountpoint is not empty
fuse: if you are sure this is safe, use the 'nonempty' mount option
Internal FUSE error, please try again.

需要加上nonempty参数







